content: Love this game! It's a difficult old school rpg that doesn't hold your hand. Explore carefully, save often. My only complaint is that the on screen controls can't be hidden permanently.
Very fun old school style RPG. Love how you create your own party from various classes. Recommend you save often
Plays exactly how i'd expect a classic RPG to play. Wish the controls were more polished but i got used to them. Keep it up!

Top quality retro rpg with unique monster battling system. The other two retro rpg's from this dev are; RPG Knight Bewitched and Knight of Heaven: Finding Light. Three hidden retro gems in the playstore.
